terian.", "Merged with: Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.); to form: Presbyterian of the South and the Presbyterian standard.", "Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.) (OCoLC)8448735", "Presbyterian of the South and the Presbyterian standard (OCoLC)8449584"], "number": ["00271764832", "10021978", "1"], "number_edition": ["1"], "number_lccn": ["10021978"], "number_reel": ["00271764832"], "numeric_shelf_id": 192102091, "online_format": ["image", "pdf", "online text"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_formats": [{"label": "MODSXML Record", "link": "//tile.loc.gov/storage-services/service/ndnp//vi/batch_vi_nipon_ver01/data/10021978/00271764832/1921020901/1921020901_1.xml"}, {"label": "MARCXML Record", "link": "//lccn.loc.gov/10021978/marcxml"}], "partof": [{"count": 675, "title": "the presbyterian of the south : [combining the] southwestern presbyterian, central presbyterian, southern presbyterian (atlanta, ga.) 1909-1931", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:the+presbyterian+of+the+south+:+%5Bcombining+the%5D+southwestern+presbyterian,+central+presbyterian,+southern+presbyterian+%28atlanta,+ga.%29+1909-1931&fo=json"}, {"count": 3203926, "title": "chronicling america", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/collections/chronicling-america/?fo=json"}, {"count": 3225157, "title": "serial and government publications division", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=partof:serial+and+government+publications+division&fo=json"}], "partof_collection": ["chronicling america"], "partof_division": ["serial and government publications division"], "partof_title": ["the presbyterian of the south : [combining the] southwestern presbyterian, central presbyterian, southern presbyterian (atlanta, ga.) 1909-1931"], "place_of_publication": "Atlanta, Ga.", "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "raw_lccn": "   10021978 ", "reel_numbers": ["00271764832"], "resources": [{"files": 18, "image": "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:vi:batch_vi_nipon_ver01:data:10021978:00271764832:1921020901:0106/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/10021978/1921-02-09/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "rights": ["<p>The Library of Congress believes that the newspapers in Chronicling America are in the public domain or have no known copyright restrictions.  Newspapers published in the United States more than 95 years ago are in the public domain in their entirety. Any newspapers in Chronicling America that were published less than 95 years ago are also believed to be in the public domain, but may contain some copyrighted third party materials. Researchers using newspapers published less than 95 years ago should be alert for modern content (for example, registered and renewed for copyright and published with notice) that may be copyrighted.  Responsibility for making an independent legal assessment of an item and securing any necessary permissions ultimately rests with persons desiring to use the item.</p>\n<p>The NEH awardee responsible for producing each digital object is presented in the Chronicling America page display, below the page image  \u2013 e.g. Image produced by the Library of Congress. For more information on current NDNP awardees, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html\">https://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "10021978, 1921-02-09, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/vi", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["richmond", "georgia", "newspapers", "virginia", "presbyterians", "united states", "fulton", "presbyterian church in the u.s", "atlanta", "presbyterian church", "atlanta (ga.)", "richmond (va.)", "presbyterian church in the u.s.", "henrico"], "subject_headings": ["Presbyterian Church in the U.S.--Newspapers", "Presbyterian Church--Georgia--Newspapers", "Presbyterian Church--Virginia--Newspapers", "Presbyterians--United States--Newspapers", "Atlanta (Ga.)--Newspapers", "Richmond (Va.)--Newspapers", "Presbyterian Church in the U.S", "Presbyterian Church", "Presbyterians", "Georgia", "Georgia--Atlanta", "United States", "Virginia", "Virginia--Richmond", "United States--Georgia--Fulton--Atlanta", "United States--Virginia--Henrico--Richmond"], "subjects": [{"atlanta": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:atlanta&fo=json"}, {"atlanta (ga.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:atlanta+%28ga.%29&fo=json"}, {"fulton": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:fulton&fo=json"}, {"georgia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:georgia&fo=json"}, {"henrico": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:henrico&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"presbyterian church": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:presbyterian+church&fo=json"}, {"presbyterian church in the u.s": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:presbyterian+church+in+the+u.s&fo=json"}, {"presbyterian church in the u.s.": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:presbyterian+church+in+the+u.s.&fo=json"}, {"presbyterians": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:presbyterians&fo=json"}, {"richmond": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:richmond&fo=json"}, {"richmond (va.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:richmond+%28va.%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"virginia": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:virginia&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-02-08T01:59:43.040Z", "title": "The Presbyterian of the South : [combining the] Southwestern Presbyterian, Central Presbyterian, Southern Presbyterian (Atlanta, Ga.), February 9, 1921", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/1921-02-09/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/10021978"], "batch": ["vi_mcqueen_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1909", "description": ["Weekly Vol. 1, no. 1 (Jan. 6, 1909)-v. 105, no. 32 (Aug. 12, 1931). Published: Richmond, Virginia <May 24, 1911-December 1922>. Issue for Aug. 14, 1912 called: v. 4, no. 33; with its issue for Sept. 4, 1912 (called: v. 86, no. 36) it assumed vol. numbering of the Charleston observer. Cf. Union list of serials. Vols. 89-92 misnumbered v. 84-87. Cf. ULS. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Imprint varies. Formed by the union of: Southern Presbyterian; Central Presbyterian, and South-western Presbyterian. Merged with: Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.); to form: Presbyterian of the South and the Presbyterian standard. Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.) (OCoLC)8448735 Presbyterian of the South and the Presbyterian standard (OCoLC)8449584"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:09.423Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-12", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-12"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [37.540759, -77.433932], "location": ["richmond", "georgia", "virginia", "united states", "fulton", "atlanta", "henrico"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-77.433932, 37.540759], "number": ["sn89053987", "sn89053990", "674", "sn89059046", "2024-01-28t09:26:30.871975", "http://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/1909-01-06/ed-1/", "microform", "2475-4528", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "10021978", "http://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/1922-12-27/ed-1/", "8449383", "library of virginia, the", "union psce", "2025-06-27t06:57:46", "online resource", "original", "1"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "chronicling america", "catalog", "the presbyterian of the south : [combining the] southwestern presbyterian, central presbyterian, southern presbyterian (atlanta, ga.) 1909-1931", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 127.05764, "shelf_id": "Newspaper BX8901 .P725", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["richmond", "georgia", "newspapers", "virginia", "presbyterians", "united states", "fulton", "presbyterian church in the u.s", "atlanta", "presbyterian church", "atlanta (ga.)", "richmond (va.)", "presbyterian church in the u.s.", "henrico"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:00:35.118Z", "title": "The Presbyterian of the South : [combining the] Southwestern Presbyterian, Central Presbyterian, Southern Presbyterian", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/10021978/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2016271271/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1909", "dates": ["[1909 TO 1931]"], "description": ["Weekly Began January 6, 1909; ceased with August 12, 1931 issue. Published: Richmond, Virginia <May 24, 1911-December 1922>. Issue for Aug. 14, 1912 called: v. 4, no. 33; with its issue for Sept. 4, 1912 (called: v. 86, no. 36) it assumed vol. numbering of the Charleston observer. Cf. Union list of serials. Vols. 89-92 misnumbered v. 84-87. Cf. ULS. Imprint varies. Formed by the union of: Southern Presbyterian; Central Presbyterian, and South-western Presbyterian. Merged with: Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.); to form: Presbyterian of the South and the Presbyterian standard. Description based on: Vol. 1, no. 1 (January 6, 1909); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2016). Latest issue consulted: Vol. 97, no. 52 (December 27, 1922) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 21, 2016). Presbyterian standard (Charlotte, N.C.)